// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1577 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d49068f0-1fb7-52bd-9279-c0313b2e7213

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
